data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning property offers a comfortable living space with an open concept layout, ideal for both family living and entertaining. Featuring 3 beds, 2 baths, plus a large den, it provides ample space for all your needs. A brand new roof provides peace of mind, and all appliances, including refrigerator, stove, microwave, washer, and dryer, are included. Water heater and HVAC are still in mint condition. The patio area is perfect for BBQs and cherished memories, and there's a built-in storage area. Located in vibrant Miami Gardens, enjoy access to public amenities and easy commuting with major highways nearby. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to call this inviting property your home. Contact listing agent to schedule a private tour. Age Code: Resale.
